data.name: teachScalingToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: 1) Home Plotter 2) move camera to upper position 3) click in picture to teach distance of top radius 4) move camera to lower position 5) click in picture to teach distance of bottom radius

data.name: teachToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: 1) Zero X,Y position 2) Mark tool position (at X=0,Y=0) 3) Move until marker is in center of camera view 4) Teach actual position as offset

data.name: teachOffsetToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: 1) switch to 'Tool coord.' (G54) 2) Zero X,Y position 3) Mark tool position (at X=0,Y=0) with tool on work piece 4) Move marker below center of camera view 5) Teach actual position as offset 6) switch to 'Cam coord.' (G59) - shows now X=0, Y=0

data.name: teachZeroPositionToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText

data.value: Set Coordinate zero with camera offset
